essing your bet(s). Please confirm if the bet was placed in Open Bets tab\",\"ERROR_CODE_BET_LAPSED_PRICE_IMPROVEMENT_TOO_LARGE\":\"The price of your selection has changed, please re-submit your bet. You can choose to automatically accept price movements by changing the setting on the \\\"Security Settings\\\" page in \\\"My Account\\\"\",\"ERROR_CODE_BET_LAPSED_PRICE_IMPROVEMENT_TOO_LARGE_V2\":\"The price of your selection has changed, please re-submit your bet. You can choose to automatically accept price improvements by enabling the \\\"Best Price Execution\\\" toggle in your \\\"Settings\\\"\",\"ERROR_CODE_BET_TAKEN_OR_LAPSED\":\"This bet may have lapsed or been matched\",\"ERROR_CODE_BONUS_NOT_AVAILABLE_FOR_BET_CONTEXT\":\"Bonus cannot be used on this selection\",\"ERROR_CODE_CANCELLED_NOT_PLACED\":\"Your {{param2}}{{param0}} bet at {{param1}} was cancelled. There was an error placing the replacement bet.\",\"ERROR_CODE_DEFAULT\":\"There was an error processing your bet(s)\",\"ERROR_CODE_ERROR_IN_MATCHER\":\"There was an error processing your bet(s). Please confirm if the bet was placed in Open Bets tab\",\"ERROR_CODE_ERROR_IN_ORDER\":\"There was an error processing your bet(s)\",\"ERROR_CODE_INSUFFICIENT_FUNDS\":\"You do not have sufficient available funds to place these bets or you have exceeded your exposure limit.\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_ACCOUNT_STATE\":\"Bet not placed. Your account may be inactive. Please contact our helpdesk.\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_BACK_LAY_COMBINATION\":\"The bet placement contains a back and a lay for the same selection at overlapping prices\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_BET_ID\":\"There was an error processing your bet(s)\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_BET_SIZE\":\"The bet has an invalid size\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_BID_TYPE\":\"There was an error processing your bet(s)\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_MIN_FILL_SIZE\":\"There was an error processing your bet(s)\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_ODDS\":\"The requested odds are invalid\",\"ERROR_CODE_INVALID_ORDER_TYPE\":\"