Date\",\"DATEOFBIRTH\":\"Date of birth\",\"FILTERBY\":\"Filter by\",\"HAND\":\"Hand\",\"HEIGHT\":\"Height (cm)\",\"LASTMATCHES\":\"Last Tournaments\",\"NATIONALITY\":\"Nationality\",\"OPPONENT\":\"Opponent\",\"RESULTS\":\"Results\",\"RESULTSANDSETS\":\"Results & Sets\",\"ROUND\":\"Round\",\"SURFACE\":\"Surface\",\"TOURNAMENT\":\"Tournament\",\"TURNEDPRO\":\"Turned pro\"},\"TITLE\":\"Head to Head\",\"TOPSCORERSTITLE\":\"Top scorers (in this competition)\"},\"HELP\":{\"CANCEL\":\"Cancel\",\"CONTINUE\":\"Continue\",\"KNOW_IT_ALL_TEXT\":\"Great, you know all you need to know, but you may need a reminder. To view this again turn help on in the settings menu.\",\"KNOW_IT_ALL_TITLE\":\"So you know it all?\",\"LETS_BET\":\"Let's Bet\",\"STEP_1_TEXT\":\"Hello {{param0}}, great to see you on the Exchange. Follow this simple guide to get familiar with the basics of betting on the Exchange.\",\"STEP_1_TITLE\":\"Welcome to Exchange Help\",\"STEP_2_TEXT\":\"Betfair uses decimal odds as they are simpler to work out and offer more flexible betting opportunities.\",\"STEP_2_TITLE\":\"Why Decimal Odds?\",\"STEP_3_TEXT\":\"A bet for is betting on a selection winning. You will return your stake multiplied by the odds if the selection wins, and you will lose your stake if it loses.\",\"STEP_3_TITLE\":\"Placing a bet - <i>Bet For</i>\",\"STEP_4_TEXT\":\"A bet against is betting on a selection not to win. You will win the stake that you lay if the selection loses, and you will payout the stake multiplied by the odds if it wins.\",\"STEP_4_TITLE\":\"Placing a bet - <i>Bet Against</i>\",\"STEP_5_TEXT\":\"You now understand the basics to bet on the Exchange, so why not get started? To view this again turn help on in the settings menu.\",\"STEP_5_TITLE\":\"What next?\"},\"I18N\":{\"BEACONS\":{\"POPUP_DESCRIPTION\":\"Betfair Beacons provide a visual indicator of significant price moves. We display beacons where prices have moved from an anchor price by <b>7.5% or more</b>.\",\"POPUP_DRIFTING_DESCRIPTION\":\"the odds on a runner have increased\",\"POPUP_MORE_INFO\":\"If you would like to know more about how our Beacons work, you can <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"https://betting.betfair.com/betfair-announcements/whats-new-on-betfair/the-betfair-beacons-new-feature-lights-up-betfair-exchange-price-moves-151123-204.html\\\">find out here</a>.\",\"POPUP_SHORTENING_DESCRIPTION\":\"the odds on a runner have decreased\"},\"CASHOUT\":{\"ACTION\":\"Cash Out\",\"AUTO_CASHOUT\":\"Auto Cash Out\",\"AUTO_CASHOUT_PLACEHOLDER\":\"Profit\",\"AUTO_CASHOUT_REMOVED\":\"Auto Cash Out removed\",\"AUTO_CASHOUT_SAVED\":\"Auto Cash Out saved\",\"CANCEL\":\"Cancel\",\"CONFIRM_ACTION\":\"Confirm\",\"CONTINUE\":\"Continue\",\"IF_PROFIT_REACHES\":\"If the profit reaches\",\"IF_PROFIT_REACHES_FULL\":\"Auto Cash Out if the profit reaches\",\"LIABILITY\":\"Liability:\",\"MAX\":{\"PROFIT\":\"Max\"},\"MIN\":{\"PROFIT\":\"Min\"},\"N_SECONDS_REMAINING\":\"{{secondsRemaining}} seconds remaining...\",\"PARTIAL_CASHOUT\":\"Partial Cash Out\",\"PLEASEWAIT\":\"Please wait while we cashout your bet\",\"PROFIT\":\"Profit:\",\"REMOVE\":\"Remove\",\"SAVE_AUTO_CASH_OUT\":\"Save Auto Cash Out\",\"WARNING\":{\"DONTSHOWAGAIN\":\"Show Cash Out confirmation\"}},\"DIALOG\":{\"MATCH_ME\":{\"INFO\":\"<span><strong>What is MatchMe?</strong></span><br><span>MatchMe is a new feature which helps you to achieve a full match when you place a bet.</span><br><br><span><strong>Why MatchMe?</strong></span><br><span>Odds can change rapidly, resulting in unwanted unmatched bets.<br><br>Think of MatchMe as a smart betting assistant which finds the best price available for you, within a range that you control.<br><br>Don’t waste time editing your unwanted unmatched bets, use MatchMe to simplify your experience and achieve a full match faster.</span>\",\"TITLE\":\"MatchMe\"}},\"GAMES_WIDGET\":{\"PLAY_DEMO\":\"Play Demo\",\"PLAY_FULL_SIZE\":\"Play Full Size\",\"PLAY_NOW\":\"Play\",\"SHOW_LESS\":\"Show less\",\"SHOW_MOR